snippet.title: Why Zach Snyder Must Fire Amber from Aquaman 2
snippet.description:
Hollywood has been going crazy over Amber Heard and Johnny Depp’s legal battle. Has Amber actually been fired from Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom? Did fans actually threaten to boycott the movie if Amber Heard is not fired? How is Zack Synder responding to furious fans? Find out on What’s Poppin’
